      <title>最高法院将审查拜登政府的“幽灵枪”规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/supreme-court-will-review-biden-administration-ghost-gun-rule</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院同意决定乔·拜登总统的政府是否可以监管自制的“幽灵枪”套件，这增加了高等法院议程上越来越多的枪支案件清单。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/supreme-court-will-review-biden-administration-ghost-gun-rule</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 13:31:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
